# Solution of Python challenge on HackerRank
# The Captain's Room
# Found at https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/py-the-captains-room/problem?isFullScreen=true
# --------------------------------------------------------------

k, arr = int(input()),list(map(int, input().split()))

myset = set(arr)

print(((sum(myset)*k)-(sum(arr)))//(k-1))